name: Ways of Being
description: As we grow, we expand our knowledge and experience of the world beyond the small, familiar beginnings we call home. As we learn, we begin to see the similarities and differences in the myriad species of our more-than-human coinhabitants, their diverse adaptations mirror our own differences in the environments we create, choose or are raised within. As you step into the world around you, look closely and you will find so many ways of being to delight in.
